<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Brunn, Bischof von Würzburg</head><p>Makulierter Teilentwurf des nächsten Briefs.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_536" id="267v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_536_r1l1"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> Bẏſchof cʒu <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_536_r1l2">Gnediger
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns ewr
                                    <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                                <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l3">von <expan>Tün<ex>n</ex>felt</expan> wegen /
                                    <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            gnaden brief wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l4"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd wiewol das
                            iſt / daʒ derſelb <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> ſwerlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l5">vvider vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                            getan hat / vnbıllıcher ſach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l6">Alſo / daʒ vvir noch die
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des gen Jm niht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchuldet</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l7">
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / yedoch ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                            vvir <add><ab facs="#facs_536_line_1576311819320_2706">ew </ab></add>
                            das vormals <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                                gnaden </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l8">heime geſecʒt vnd ewr gnade damit geeret / als
                            vvol cʒimlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l10">iſt / Vnd alſo <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            vvir <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>rıchtıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / als <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l11"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jm vnd vns
                            beredt vnd gemacht hat für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l12">vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch
                            gencʒlich ſtet <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l13">wo etc <app><note place="inline">Ad <expan>manda<ex>tum</ex></expan>
<expan>Erh<ex>ardi</ex></expan>
<expan>Schurſt<ex>ab</ex></expan></note></app>
</ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_536" id="267v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan>, Byschof czu
                                    <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr
                                    <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                                <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Tün<ex>n</ex>felt</expan> wegen,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            gnaden brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>; und wiewol das ist,
                            daz derselb <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> swerlich wider uns und die
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> getan hat unbillicher sach, also
                            daz wir noch die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des gen im niht
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schuldet</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, yedoch so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                            wir <add>ew</add> das vormals heime geseczt und ewr gnade damit geeret,
                            als wol czimlich ist, und also <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                    <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>richtigu<ex>n</ex>g,</expan> als <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im und uns beredt und gemacht hat, für
                            uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch genczlich stet
                                    <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>on gev<ex>er</ex>de.</expan> Und wo etc. <app>
<note place="inline">Ad <expan>mand<ex>atum</ex></expan>
<expan>Erh<ex>ardi</ex></expan>
<expan>Schurst<ex>ab.</ex></expan></note>
</app></del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
